    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior has substantial rust spots, major paint peeling, and several large dents. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and there are noticeable leaks that need immediate repair. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This car is best suited as a project vehicle or for parts, and it is priced to reflect the extensive repairs needed to make it roadworthy again.",
